# rename(_:)

**Instance Method**

Changes a title.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor optional func rename(_ sender: Any?)
```

## Handling data commands

- **duplicate(_:)**: Duplicates data.
- **export(_:)**: Exports data in different file formats or to other apps.
- **move(_:)**: Prompts a person to specify a new location and moves data to that location.
